cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.LG 

This paper is about interactive spoken content retrieval, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, such as deep Q-learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SD (Sound).
